common-butterfly.name: Common Butterfly
common-butterfly.description: You caught a common butterfly! They often flutter by!

yellow-butterfly.name: Yellow Butterfly
yellow-butterfly.description: You caught a yellow butterfly! Shouldn't all BUTTERflies be yellow?

tiger-butterfly.name: Tiger Butterfly
tiger-butterfly.description: You caught a tiger butterfly! I've earned my stripes!

peacock-butterfly.name: Peacock Butterfly
peacock-butterfly.description: You caught a peacock butterfly! Now it's my turn to strut my stuff!

common-bluebottle.name: Common Bluebottle
common-bluebottle.description: You caught a common bluebottle! I'll put it in a rare green jar!

paper-kite-butterfly.name: Paper Kite Butterfly
paper-kite-butterfly.description: You caught a paper kite butterfly! Do I read it, fly it, or spread it on toast?

great-purple-emperor.name: Great Purple Emperor
great-purple-emperor.description: You caught a great purple emperor! Its purple reign is over now!

monarch-butterfly.name: Monarch Butterfly
monarch-butterfly.description: You caught a monarch butterfly! Guess the butterflies are a democracy now!

emperor-butterfly.name: Emperor Butterfly
emperor-butterfly.description: You caught an emperor butterfly! It's not your average monarch!

agrias-butterfly.name: Agrias Butterfly
agrias-butterfly.description: You caught an agrias butterfly! I wonder if it finds me disagrias-able?

rajah-brooke-birdwing.name: Rajah Brooke's Birdwing
rajah-brooke-birdwing.description: You caught a Rajah Brooke's birdwing! Nothing else I'd rajah be doing!

queen-alexandra-birdwing.name: Queen Alexandra's Birdwing
queen-alexandra-birdwing.description: You caught a Queen Alexandra's birdwing! That's a feather in my cap!

moth.name: Moth
moth.description: You caught a moth! And I had a ball doing it!

atlas-moth.name: Atlas Moth
atlas-moth.description: You caught an Atlas moth! I bet it never gets lost!

madagascan-sunset-moth.name: Madagascan Sunset Moth
madagascan-sunset-moth.description: You caught a Madagascan sunset moth! Wow, you're not from around here!

long-locust.name: Long Locust
long-locust.description: You caught a long locust! Or, as I call it, a looooocust.

migratory-locust.name: Migratory Locust
migratory-locust.description: You caught a migratory locust! Things just went south for this guy!

rice-grasshopper.name: Rice Grasshopper
rice-grasshopper.description: You caught a rice grasshopper! I've been looking for a gluten-free alternative...

grasshopper.name: Grasshopper
grasshopper.description: You caught a grasshopper! They're a grass act!

cricket.name: Cricket
cricket.description: You caught a cricket! What a chirp thrill!

bell-cricket.name: Bell Cricket
bell-cricket.description: You caught a bell cricket! It would make a great bellhop!

mantis.name: Mantis
mantis.description: You caught a mantis! Man, 'tis so cool!

orchid-mantis.name: Orchid Mantis
orchid-mantis.description: You caught an orchid mantis! Our friendship is blooming!

honeybee.name: Honeybee
honeybee.description: You caught a honeybee! Ah, sweet success!

wasp.name: Wasp
wasp.description: You caught a wasp! That's gotta sting...

brown-cicada.name: Brown Cicada
brown-cicada.description: You caught a brown cicada! Now it probably feels blue, cicada.

robust-cicada.name: Robust Cicada
robust-cicada.description: You caught a robust cicada! It DOES seem pretty lively!

giant-cicada.name: Giant Cicada
giant-cicada.description: You caught a giant cicada! I guess it's PRETTY big...

walker-cicada.name: Walker Cicada
walker-cicada.description: You caught a walker cicada! Pffft... I walk all the time and no one calls me "Walker <Player>."

evening-cicada.name: Evening Cicada
evening-cicada.description: You caught an evening cicada! Better than an odding cicada...

cicada-shell.name: Cicada Shell
cicada-shell.description: I found a cicada shell! I'm glad the little guy came out of it!

red-dragonfly.name: Red Dragonfly
red-dragonfly.description: You caught a red dragonfly! Didn't even have to roll for initiative!

darner-dragonfly.name: Darner Dragonfly
darner-dragonfly.description: You caught a darner dragonfly! It better watch its mouth!

banded-dragonfly.name: Banded Dragonfly
banded-dragonfly.description: I did it! Did you see that? You caught a banded dragonfly!

damselfly.name: Damselfly
damselfly.description: You caught a damselfly! Now it's a damselfly in distress!

firefly.name: Firefly
firefly.description: You caught a firefly! I'm on fire now!

mole-cricket.name: Mole Cricket
mole-cricket.description: You caught a mole cricket! I really dug it!

pondskater.name: Pondskater
pondskater.description: You caught a pondskater! Wonder if it can do a pond ollie...

diving-beetle.name: Diving Beetle
diving-beetle.description: You caught a diving beetle! Now I'm making a splash!

giant-water-bug.name: Giant Water Bug
giant-water-bug.description: You caught a giant water bug! It should've stayed in the water!

stinkbug.name: Stinkbug
stinkbug.description: You caught a stinkbug! It lives up to its name!

man-faced-stink-bug.name: Man-Faced Stink Bug
man-faced-stink-bug.description: You caught a man-faced stink bug! Reminds me of my uncle!

ladybug.name: Ladybug
ladybug.description: You caught a ladybug! Sorry to disturb you, ma'am.

tiger-beetle.name: Tiger Beetle
tiger-beetle.description: You caught a tiger beetle! I pounced first!

jewel-beetle.name: Jewel Beetle
jewel-beetle.description: You caught a jewel beetle! It's a real gem!

violin-beetle.name: Violin Beetle
violin-beetle.description: You caught a violin beetle! Apparently I'm as fit as a fiddle!

citrus-long-horned-beetle.name: Citrus Long-Horned Beetle
citrus-long-horned-beetle.description: You caught a citrus long-horned beetle! Orange you happy for me?

rosalia-batesi-beetle.name: Rosalia Batesi Beetle
rosalia-batesi-beetle.description: You caught a rosalia batesi beetle! That's easier to do than say!

blue-weevil-beetle.name: Blue Weevil Beetle
blue-weevil-beetle.description: You caught a blue weevil beetle! It's the lesser of blue weevils!

dung-beetle.name: Dung Beetle
dung-beetle.description: You caught a dung beetle! This species likes feces!

earth-boring-dung-beetle.name: Earth-Boring Dung Beetle
earth-boring-dung-beetle.description: You caught an earth-boring dung beetle! It's not boring at all!

scarab-beetle.name: Scarab Beetle
scarab-beetle.description: You caught a scarab beetle! It's just a dung beetle with better hobbies.

drone-beetle.name: Drone Beetle
drone-beetle.description: You caught a drone beetle! Shouldn't you have more propellers?

goliath-beetle.name: Goliath Beetle
goliath-beetle.description: You caught a goliath beetle! Am I a legend or what?

saw-stag.name: Saw Stag
saw-stag.description: You caught a saw stag! Now I can't unsee it!

miyama-stag.name: Miyama Stag
miyama-stag.description: You caught a miyama stag! Its mandibles are jaw-dropping!

giant-stag.name: Giant Stag
giant-stag.description: Whoaaa! You caught a giant stag! I'm gonna need way bigger pockets...

rainbow-stag.name: Rainbow Stag
rainbow-stag.description: You caught a rainbow stag! Its rainbow armor is so shiny!

cyclommatus-stag.name: Cyclommatus Stag
cyclommatus-stag.description: You caught a cyclommatus stag! Those mandibles are a mouthful!

golden-stag.name: Golden Stag
golden-stag.description: Wooooow! You caught a golden stag! Does this mean I can retire?

giraffe-stag.name: Giraffe Stag
giraffe-stag.description: You caught a giraffe stag! Does that make it a longhorn?

horned-dynastid.name: Horned Dynastid
horned-dynastid.description: You caught a horned dynastid! I'd hate to hear it honk that schnoz!

horned-atlas.name: Horned Atlas
horned-atlas.description: You caught a horned atlas! I didn't even need a map!

horned-elephant.name: Horned Elephant
horned-elephant.description: You caught a horned elephant! I think it's too small to ride...

horned-hercules.name: Horned Hercules
horned-hercules.description: You caught a horned hercules! Guess I was stronger!

walking-stick.name: Walking Stick
walking-stick.description: You caught a walking stick! Check out its walking schtick! Look, these are the jokes, OK?

walking-leaf.name: Walking Leaf
walking-leaf.description: You caught a walking leaf! It seems to be taking it in stride!

bagworm.name: Bagworm
bagworm.description: You caught a bagworm! Guess I'm a bragworm!

ant.name: Ant
ant.description: You caught an ant! TELL ME WHERE THE QUEEN IS!

hermit-crab.name: Hermit Crab
hermit-crab.description: You caught a hermit crab! I think it wanted to be left alone!

wharf-roach.name: Wharf Roach
wharf-roach.description: You caught a wharf roach! This water-loving roach has no pier!

fly.name: Fly
fly.description: You caught a fly! I was just wingin' it...

mosquito.name: Mosquito
mosquito.description: You caught a mosquito! It's itching for a fight!

flea.name: Flea
flea.description: You caught a flea! The curse is lifted.

snail.name: Snail
snail.description: You caught a snail! It's...not much to brag about.

pill-bug.name: Pill Bug
pill-bug.description: You caught a pill bug! That's a tough act to swallow!

centipede.name: Centipede
centipede.description: You caught a centipede! 99 more and I'll have a dollarpede!

spider.name: Spider
spider.description: You caught a spider! I spied 'er first!

tarantula.name: Tarantula
tarantula.description: You caught a tarantula! This situation just got hairy!

scorpion.name: Scorpion
scorpion.description: You caught a scorpion! It was a sting operation!
